title: France 30 Year bond-Yield
description: France 30 Year Bond Yield was 3.07 percent on Monday November 7, according to over-the-counter interbank yield quotes for this government bond maturity. Historically, the France 30 Year bond-Yield reached an all time high of 5.07 in September of 2008. This page includes a chart with historical data for France 30Y.
